## Localization Invariants

{{#HAS_LOCALIZATION}}
### No hardcoded user-facing strings
- **Grep**: `{{localization_grep}}`
- **Why**: Breaks localization
- **Fix**: Add key to localization files, use generated constants
- **Exception**: Debug-only strings, format strings in non-UI code
{{/HAS_LOCALIZATION}}

## Design System Invariants

{{#HAS_DESIGN_SYSTEM}}
### No hardcoded colors
- **Grep**: `{{color_grep}}`
- **Why**: Bypasses design system, breaks dark mode
- **Fix**: Use design system color constants

### No hardcoded font sizes
- **Grep**: `{{font_grep}}`
- **Why**: Bypasses typography system
- **Fix**: Use design system typography
{{/HAS_DESIGN_SYSTEM}}

## Code Quality Invariants

### No optional booleans for tri-state — use enums
- **Grep**: `{{optional_bool_grep}}`
- **Why**: `Bool?` (true/false/nil) creates ambiguous logic
- **Fix**: Define an enum with explicit named cases
- **Exception**: API parameters that simply pass through optionals

### No force unwraps in production code
- **Grep**: `{{force_unwrap_grep}}`
- **Why**: Runtime crash risk
- **Fix**: Use safe unwrapping with defaults
- **Exception**: Truly guaranteed values (with comment explaining why)

### No `print()` — use structured logging
- **Grep**: `{{print_grep}}`
- **Why**: Not captured in logging infrastructure
- **Fix**: Use proper logging framework

{{#HAS_CODEGEN}}
### Generated files are never manually edited
- **Grep**: Changes to files containing `{{codegen_marker}}`
- **Why**: Overwritten on next generation
- **Fix**: Edit source file, then run generation command
{{/HAS_CODEGEN}}

## Refactoring Invariants

### All references updated when renaming
- **Check**: `rg "oldName" {{file_pattern}}` returns 0 results (excluding generated files)
- **Why**: Missed references cause build failures or dead code
- **Fix**: Search and update all: production, tests, mocks, DI registrations

### Unused code removed after refactoring
- **Check**: No orphaned files, unreferenced properties, or dead imports
- **Why**: Prevents bloat and confusion
- **Fix**: Search for usages, delete if unreferenced

